{"tid":2348837,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"跨年晚會︱劉嘉玲開金口唱歌　梁朝偉公開力讚老婆：很好！","createTime":"2021-01-01T05:28:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T07:27:49.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"176ea9673e70b503230c3a1e6b64533c4605de17","tid":2348837,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:28:02.000Z","msg":"內地「東方衛視」今年跨年演唱會邀請了不少圈中夫妻檔出席，其中一對就是劉嘉玲同梁朝偉，令不少網友非常期待。而就在剛剛劉嘉玲率先現身，竟然大開金口唱歌，不過並不是同老公梁朝偉共同合唱，而是同台灣歌手張信哲、內地演員黃景瑜、李澤鋒合唱多首歌曲，包括《有一點動心》、《親愛的密人》、《你是如此難以忘記》，表演非常精彩。<br />\n<br />\n不過就在她同李澤鋒唱完歌之後，在空隙的時間她就拿起咪高峰同大家打招呼，講出一句：「大家好」，沒想到此時咪高峰沒有開聲音，顯得她非常尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n接着老公粱朝偉就出場宣傳電影《獵狐行動》，此時主持人就把握機會問到他劉嘉玲的歌聲如何時，他就一臉顯得好尷尬，隨後就笑言力讚老婆：「很好」，相信劉嘉玲聽到一定好開心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201231/421458927838826496832651.jpeg/GDrejnHC0B1-_1fr4FLfTlpnGXq5bsr35z2q8uc9qvI?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201231%2F421458927838826496832651.jpeg%2FGDrejnHC0B1-_1fr4FLfTlpnGXq5bsr35z2q8uc9qvI%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=7f18aa35&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201231/421459344010383360074286.jpeg/6Q09WGqOjamfrGQIYPdZXE8vn3QpgADJaFGzJWhRsyU?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201231%2F421459344010383360074286.jpeg%2F6Q09WGqOjamfrGQIYPdZXE8vn3QpgADJaFGzJWhRsyU%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=e4b76960&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201231/421459705421762560926517.jpeg/4W12DnXwAyP85pBip4GavGRJQ5Rup1TAXZKB_V2Sgf0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201231%2F421459705421762560926517.jpeg%2F4W12DnXwAyP85pBip4GavGRJQ5Rup1TAXZKB_V2Sgf0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=12e84350&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ea46b5163af62073d8c41b8fee9a974b04c14cc","tid":2348837,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T07:11:36